Approach to economic analysis in critical care.

Kyeremanteng K(1), Wan C(2), D'Egidio G(3), Neilipovitz D(4).

Author information:
(1)The Ottawa Hospital, Ottawa, Ontario, Canada. Electronic address: 
kkyeremanteng@toh.ca.
(2)University of Ottawa, Ottawa, Ontario, Canada. Electronic address: 
cwan062@uottawa.ca.
(3)The Ottawa Hospital, Ottawa, Ontario, Canada. Electronic address: 
gdegidio@toh.ca.
(4)The Ottawa Hospital, Ottawa, Ontario, Canada. Electronic address: 
